    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
        <seg>## Basic animation</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN" changeid="aceway" changedate="20160330T033807Z" creationid="aceway" creationdate="20160330T033807Z">
        <seg>## 简单动画</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
        <seg>**Parameter 1** - Name of this animation, nothing more.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN" changeid="aceway@qq.com" changedate="20160330T125254Z" creationid="aceway@qq.com" creationdate="20160330T125243Z">
        <seg>**参数 1** - 仅仅是这个动画的名字.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
        <seg>**Parameter 2** - The property concerned.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN" changeid="aceway@qq.com" changedate="20160330T125326Z" creationid="aceway@qq.com" creationdate="20160330T125251Z">
        <seg>**参数 2** - 关注是属性.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
        <seg>**Parameter 3** - Frames per second requested: highest FPS possible in this animation.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN" changeid="aceway@qq.com" changedate="20160330T125611Z" creationid="aceway@qq.com" creationdate="20160330T125611Z">
        <seg>**参数 3** - 每秒请求的帧数: 这个动画的最大 FPS(Frames Per Second).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
        <seg>**Parameter 4** - Type of change.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN" changeid="aceway@qq.com" changedate="20160330T125631Z" creationid="aceway@qq.com" creationdate="20160330T125631Z">
        <seg>**参数 4** - 修改类型.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
        <seg>//Create a box</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN" changeid="aceway@qq.com" changedate="20160330T125052Z" creationid="aceway@qq.com" creationdate="20160330T125052Z">
        <seg>//创建一个盒子</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
        <seg>//Here... your basic scene as before: [scene, light, camera]</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN" changeid="aceway@qq.com" changedate="20160330T125043Z" creationid="aceway@qq.com" creationdate="20160330T125043Z">
        <seg>//这儿... 作为基础场景的: [scene, light, camera]</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
        <seg>An Animation is defined by various properties and a collection of keys.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN" changeid="aceway@qq.com" changedate="20160330T123125Z" creationid="aceway@qq.com" creationdate="20160330T123125Z">
        <seg>一个动画由各种属性和关键帧定义</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
        <seg>Animations
---
# Animation
Your scene is beginning to look great, but it is very static.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN" changeid="aceway" changedate="20160330T033049Z" creationid="aceway" creationdate="20160330T031952Z">
        <seg>动画 你的场景开始看起来很棒了，但它仍然是静态的。
---
# Animation
Your scene is beginning to look great, but it is very static.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
        <seg>First, create our Animation object:</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN" changeid="aceway@qq.com" changedate="20160330T125144Z" creationid="aceway@qq.com" creationdate="20160330T125144Z">
        <seg>第一个步, 创建我们的动画对象:</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
        <seg>Here we want to scale an object on the X axis, so it will be “scaling.x”.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN" changeid="aceway@qq.com" changedate="20160330T125508Z" creationid="aceway@qq.com" creationdate="20160330T125508Z">
        <seg>此处我们希望在X轴方向放大对象，所以是“scaling.x”.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
        <seg>Much information is in the parameters:</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN" changeid="aceway@qq.com" changedate="20160330T125201Z" creationid="aceway@qq.com" creationdate="20160330T125201Z">
        <seg>许多信息在参数里</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
        <seg>Our goal: move this “box1”.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN" changeid="aceway@qq.com" changedate="20160330T125117Z" creationid="aceway@qq.com" creationdate="20160330T125117Z">
        <seg>我们的目标：移动这个“box1”.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
        <seg>The animation is based on objects called Animation (!!).</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN" changeid="aceway@qq.com" changedate="20160330T123040Z" creationid="aceway@qq.com" creationdate="20160330T094901Z">
        <seg>基于众多物体对象的动画也叫电影片段</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
        <seg>The first is to define a collection of keys and defining your object's situation at each key.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN" changeid="aceway" changedate="20160330T033542Z" creationid="aceway" creationdate="20160330T033530Z">
        <seg>第一种方式是定义关键帧集合，并且每帧定义好你的对象物的状态。</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
        <seg>The second way is for more complex animations, when you change animation code at run time.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN" changeid="aceway" changedate="20160330T033700Z" creationid="aceway" creationdate="20160330T033700Z">
        <seg>第二种方式可以定义更复杂的动画，在运行是改变动画代码。</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
        <seg>There are two primary ways of doing animations in your scene.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN" changeid="aceway" changedate="20160330T033350Z" creationid="aceway" creationdate="20160330T033350Z">
        <seg>有两种主要的方式实现场景动画。</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
        <seg>This can be any mesh property, depending upon what you want to change.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN" changeid="aceway@qq.com" changedate="20160330T125401Z" creationid="aceway@qq.com" creationdate="20160330T125401Z">
        <seg>这个可以是任意的网格属性，取决与你要修改什么.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
        <seg>To achieve today’s animated scene, we begin by creating our environment:</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN" changeid="aceway@qq.com" changedate="20160330T124953Z" creationid="aceway@qq.com" creationdate="20160330T124953Z">
        <seg>为了实现今天的动画场景，我们开始创基础环境:</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
        <seg>To put dynamics in it, we are going to learn how to tell your computer to move your meshes in any way you choose.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN" changeid="aceway" changedate="20160330T033249Z" creationid="aceway" creationdate="20160330T033249Z">
        <seg>为了给它注入动态，我们将开始学习如何控制电脑来按照人指定的方式移动你创建的网格对象。</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
